SOURCE4 RAYTRACER
William Brown (whb2107)

Raytracer which completes all of phases one and two, all but the BVH in phase
three, and adds depth of field as well. Everything conforms to the grammar given
in the assignment. To activate antialiasing, use the option:

o a N

Where N is the number of subsamples to take for each pixel. To activate depth of
field, use the option:

o d N A F

Where N is the number of subsamples to take for each pixel, A is the aperture
and F is the focal length. Sample scenes are provided in the scenes/ directory.

All output images are written to test.exr.
